      • net.automatalib:automata-api:jar:0.4.0-SNAPSHOT (compile)
        AutomataLib :: API

        Description: This artifact contains the API of AutomataLib, which mainly consists of interfaces for the various concepts and automaton models supported by the AutomataLib core. In addition to that, it also defines some fundamental classes for dealing with words of symbols.

        URL: http://misberner.github.io/automatalib/maven-site/0.4.0-SNAPSHOT/automata-api

        Project License: GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3, 29 June 2007

      • net.automatalib:automata-core:jar:0.4.0-SNAPSHOT (compile)
        AutomataLib :: Core

        Description: The core artifact of AutomataLib. This library contains concrete implementations for many of the automaton model interfaces defined in the API artifact, as well as abstract base classes that facilitate implementing new automaton model classes. Note that concrete algorithms (traversal, reachability analysis etc.) are not in the scope of this artifact.

        URL: http://misberner.github.io/automatalib/maven-site/0.4.0-SNAPSHOT/automata-core

        Project License: GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3, 29 June 2007

    • net.automatalib:automata-util:jar:0.4.0-SNAPSHOT (compile)
      AutomataLib :: Utilities

      Description: This artifact provides various common utility operations for analyzing and manipulating automata and graphs, such as traversal, minimization and copying.

      URL: http://misberner.github.io/automatalib/maven-site/0.4.0-SNAPSHOT/automata-util

      Project License: GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3, 29 June 2007
